{"tid":1222433,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今次除左撒送中之外,仲要爭取削警權","createTime":"2019-06-14T12:19:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T13:15:30.000Z","uid":188176,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9ad72325327ba89fcb22401c29fee22a81296354","tid":1222433,"uid":188176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T12:19:52.000Z","msg":"一日警權過大,一日香港人都會比人欺壓<br />\n要諗辦法爭取美國用人權法制裁禿鷹同盧偉聰<br />\n迫佢地設立第三方監管機制<br />\n因為警隊入面絕大多數都係罪犯<br />\n自己人查自己人係無撚用<br />\n要令警隊入面既罪犯可以由第三方監管<br />\n嚴重時要上法庭而唔係而家難到登天咁<br />\n所有器材,編制都要規管(雖然之後警犬都唔會買到外國武器)<br />\n唔可以再好似14年畜龍仲有NUMBER係甲<br />\n19年就特登抹走等你追究唔到班罪犯<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">要好堅決,而家既警隊入面絕大多數都係罪犯<br />\n唔好再講咩大家都係香港人<br />\n咁多年香港警犬愈黎愈多,治安反而愈黎愈差<br />\n一定要理順佢地由警犬變番警隊!<br />\n今次美國出埋手,BARGAIN 就要狠一D<br />\n唔可以令佢地再有成魔一日!</span></span>"},{"pid":"238aa9e99df186a5b0027c3a36efd095953c85c3","tid":1222433,"uid":160605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T12:21:02.000Z","msg":"爭取老廉同監警恢復大權，拉晒班仆街去坐，最好上埋國際法庭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32dec788e43affd43492e60ce8f20cdb27db2c8d","tid":1222433,"uid":188176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T13:15:30.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}